<SYNC Start=456860><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457020><P Class=KRCC>
비켜! 내가 하겠다!!
<SYNC Start=458230><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P Class=KRCC>
제길!!
<SYNC Start=469060><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=475990><P Class=KRCC>
