<SYNC Start=983540><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=988130><P Class=KRCC>
코난이다!
<SYNC Start=989340><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=993440><P Class=KRCC>
